Nazario_recent,2023,"Wed, 25 Oct 2023 20:16:00 -0600",Reminder : Overdue Payment Notification !,"To view this email as a web page, go to the link below, or copy and paste it into your browser's address window. URL Overdue Payment Reminder ! We&#39;re reaching out because you&#39;ve missed your payment of $45.00. You&#39;ll need to complete the steps below to avoid your service(s) being limited from 28 Octobre 2023. What do you need to do? To keep your service(s) connected, make a manual payment of $45.00, then update your payment details for next time. There&#39;s a couple of ways to do this: 1. Using URL My Optus app on your phone 2. Logging into URL My Account URL Pay Now Got Device Protect Insurance? You&#39;ll remain covered, including your renewal into next month, but your cover may end if your account isn&#39;t paid. Check My Optus app or My Account to see if you&#39;re covered. For more important information visit Optus.com.au/Paymentinfo. Need support? We understand that unexpected events and expenses can make it difficult to keep up with regular payments. If you&#39;re having trouble paying your Optus service(s), visit Optus.com.au/FinancialHardship or get in touch with us at Optus.com.au/Contactus. We&#39;re here to help you stay connected. Already made this payment? That&#39;s great, you&#39;re all set. Thanks, Your Optus Team This email was sent by: Optus 1 Lyonpark Road Macquarie Park, NSW, 2113, Australia. THIS IS A SYSTEM GENERATED EMAIL. PLEASE DO NOT REPLY TO THIS MESSAGE ---------------------------------------- This email was sent by: KundeService-Spotify yh-gtrfe yhtg, MA, 5454, Denmark We respect your right to privacy - visit the following URL to view our policy. ( URL ) ---------------------------------------- Visit the following URL to manage your subscriptions. ( URL ) Visit the following URL to update your profile. ( URL ) Visit the following URL to unsubscribe. ( URL )",1,"Reminder : Overdue Payment Notification ! To view this email as a web