Nazario_recent,2024,"Sun, 04 Aug 2024 08:23:12 -0600",Your Debit Card is Expiring Soon–Verify Your Details,"Having trouble viewing this email? URL View Online URL URL Dear JOSE O NAZARIO: Your debit card ending in 2864 is expiring soon, so we’re getting a new one ready for you. Don’t worry—you can continue to use you current card until the last day of the expiring month. Your new card should arrive in about 2-3 weeks. We’ll ship it to: 2160 GREENVIEW DR ANN ARBOR MI 48103-6112 If this address is incorrect, please contact us as soon as possible at tel:18009723030 800-972-3030 , Monday through Friday 8 a.m. to 6 p.m., and Saturday 10 a.m. to 4 p.m., ET. Stay in the loop through the mobile app! If you use the app^1, we’ll notify you as soon as your card starts making its way to you. To monitor its progress: 1. Log in to the mobile app. 2. Find the checking account associated with your card. 3. Tap the three dots next to your account, then Manage Card. 4. Select the card from the list, then tap Card Tracker. You can update how you get notified by going to Profile (the person icon) then tap Alerts > Manage Alerts > Security > Security Alerts. Don’t have the app? Explore the possibilities! You’ll get the benefit of the Card Tracker notifications, plus security and account alerts, mobile check deposit, Zelle(R) and more. It’s like having your own personal branch right inside your pocket, 24/7. Here’s how to get started: 1. Download the app for free from your device’s app store. 2. Open the app. 3. If you already use online banking, you can use the same User ID and password to log in. If you don’t have a User ID and password, tap Sign Up and follow the prompts. It’s that easy! URL URL URL URL We’re here to help. If you have any questions, you can message us 24/7 in to the mobile app or online banking, or call us at tel:18009723030 800-972-3030 , Monday through Friday 8 a.m. to 6 p.m., and Saturday 10 a.m. to 4 p.m., ET. Thank you for banking with us. URL URL URL URL URL URL URL 1. Subject to URL Digital Services User Agreement terms and conditions. Zelle and the Zelle related mar",1,"Your Debit Card is Expiring Soon–Verify Your Details Having trouble viewing this email? URL View Online URL URL Dear JOSE O NAZARIO: Your debit card ending in 2864 is expiring soon, so we’re getting a new one ready for you. Don’t worry—you can continue to use you current card until the last day of the expiring month. Your new card should arrive in about 2-3 weeks. We’ll ship it to: 2160 GREENVIEW DR ANN ARBOR MI 48103-6112 If this address is incorrect, please contact us as soon as possible at tel:18009723030 800-972-3030 , Monday through Friday 8 a.m. to 6 p.m., and Saturday 10 a.m. to 4 p.m., ET. Stay in the loop through the mobile app! If you use the app^1, we’ll notify you as soon as your card starts making its way to you. To monitor its progress: 1. Log in to the mobile app. 2. Find the checking account associated with your card. 3. Tap the three dots next to your account, then Manage Card. 4. Select the card from the list, then tap Card Tracker. You can update how you get notified by going to Profile (the person icon) then tap Alerts > Manage Alerts > Security > Security Alerts. Don’t have the app? Explore the possibilities! You’ll get the benefit of the Card Tracker notifications, plus security and account alerts, mobile check deposit, Zelle(R) and more. It’s like having your own personal branch right inside your pocket, 24/7. Here’s how to get started: 1. Download the app for free from your device’s app store. 2. Open the app. 3. If you already use online banking, you can use the same User ID and password to log in. If you don’t have a User ID and password, tap Sign Up and follow the prompts. It’s that easy! URL URL URL URL We’re here to help. If you have any questions, you can message us 24/7 in to the mobile app or online banking, or call us at tel:18009723030 800-972-3030 , Monday through Friday 8 a.m. to 6 p.m., and Saturday 10 a.m. to 4 p.m., 