Nazario_recent,2025,"Mon, 21 Apr 2025 14:13:13 -0700 (PDT)",FW: RE: Successful ACHDirect Deposit (Trans ID:67YT30O67UT) Completed.,"Remittance Document Shared With You You have received the following item: ACH-Direct deposit #58674 confirmed [ Open ]( URL ) Google LLC, 1600 Amphitheatre Parkway, Mountain View, CA 94043, USA You have received this email because a file located in Google Drive was shared with you. -----Original Message----- From: ""gschmidt@pmz.com"" <gschmidt@pmz.com> Sent: Tuesday, December 8, 2020 9:49am To: westcoast@mindspring.com Cc: ""gschmidt@pmz.com"" <gschmidt@pmz.com> Subject: RE: Inquiry for use as a comparable, / 21673 Fourth Ave. Stevenson, Closed, 08/24/20 Everything seemed in perfect order.... I did not list the property and I let title do their job on the MLS data. The seller had done huge repairs so the homes on the property were basically brand new condition. I believe we asked for and received around 850 closing credit for some flooring that seemed soft in an area of the home Thanks Gary -----Original Message----- From: westcoast@mindspring.com Sent: Friday, December 4, 2020 8:20am To: ""Gary Schmidt"" <gschmidt@pmz.com> Subject: Inquiry for use as a comparable, / 21673 Fourth Ave. Stevenson, Closed, 08/24/20 Hello Gary, David here at West Coast Appraisal Services. West Coast Appraisal Services would like to use 21673 Fourth Ave. in Stevinson, for a comparable. Can you verify that the data in MLS is correct? Can you tell us if there were any needed repairs discovered during inspections that were not noted in MLS? Can you tell us if there were any sale concessions that were not noted in MLS? Is there anything else about the property or the transaction you think we should know? Thank you for your time and any information that you can give us would be appreciated. David Georgis Data Verification Specialist for West Coast Appraisal Services [ westcoast@mindspring.com ]( mailto:westcoast@mindspring.com ) Leslyn Georgis AR027135 Certified Residential Real Estate Appraiser leslyngeorgis@earthlink.net text/cell: 209-652-0048 Office: 209-526-5331 PO Box 4977, Modesto, CA 95352",1,"FW: RE: Successful ACHDirect Deposit (Trans ID:67YT30O67UT) Completed. Remittance Document Shared With You You have received the following item: ACH-Direct deposit #58674 confirmed [ Open ]( URL ) Google LLC, 1600 Amphitheatre Parkway, Mountain View, CA 94043, USA You have received this email because a file located in Google Drive was shared with you. -----Original Message----- From: ""gschmidt@pmz.com"" <gschmidt@pmz.com> Sent: Tuesday, December 8, 2020 9:49am To: westcoast@mindspring.com Cc: ""gschmidt@pmz.com"" <gschmidt@pmz.com> Subject: RE: Inquiry for use as a comparable, / 21673 Fourth Ave. Stevenson, Closed, 08/24/20 Everything seemed in perfect order.... I did not list the property and I let title do their job on the MLS data. The seller had done huge repairs so the homes on the property were basically brand new condition. I believe we asked for and received around 850 closing credit for some flooring that seemed soft in an area of the home Thanks Gary -----Original Message----- From: westcoast@mindspring.com Sent: Friday, December 4, 2020 8:20am To: ""Gary Schmidt"" <gschmidt@pmz.com> Subject: Inquiry for use as a comparable, / 21673 Fourth Ave. Stevenson, Closed, 08/24/20 Hello Gary, David here at West Coast Appraisal Services. West Coast Appraisal Services would like to use 21673 Fourth Ave. in Stevinson, for a comparable. Can you verify that the data in MLS is correct? Can you tell us if there were any needed repairs discovered during inspections that were not noted in MLS? Can you tell us if there were any sale concessions that were not noted in MLS? Is there anything else about the property or the transaction you think we should know? Thank you for your time and any information that you can give us would be appreciated. David Georgis Data Verification Specialist for West Coast Appraisal Services [ westcoast@mindspring.com ]( mailto:westcoast@mindspring.com ) Leslyn Georgis AR027135 Certified Residential Real Estate Appraiser leslyngeorgis@earthlink.net text/cell: 209-652-0048 Office: 209-526-5331 PO Box 4977, Modesto, CA 95352"
