t have been tampered with, or that it might not come from the supposed sender. 3 Simply click on the red ribbon icon and choose the option to view the digital identity or the certificate to verify the sender's digital identity. Disclaimer | nedbank.co.za | Contact us T & Cs apply. Nedbank Ltd Reg No 1951/000009/06. Licensed financial services and registered credit provider (NCRCP16)."
