Nazario_recent,2025,"Fri, 26 Sep 2025 13:54:29 +0000 (UTC)",We have received an online order placed under Order #4118158 for medication,"CVS PHARMACY ********************************** Order Held — Prescription Required ********************************** Please read this important notice about your recent online order Dear Customer, We have received an online order placed under Order # *4118158* for medication totaling approximately *$400.00*. The item(s) you ordered are classified as prescription-only and cannot be released without a valid, current prescription on file. *Important:* This medication requires a valid prescription under state and federal law. Dispensing or possessing this medication without a lawful prescription is prohibited and may constitute a criminal offense. To complete your order and schedule pickup, please provide one of the following as soon as possible: * A copy of a current prescription faxed or uploaded to our secure portal * Your prescriber’s name and phone number so we may verify the prescription directly If we do not receive a valid prescription within *7 business days* , the order will be cancelled and any authorized hold will be released in accordance with our policies. Upload Prescription ( # ) Contact Us ( # ) If you believe you received this message in error, or you wish to dispute or cancel the order, please contact our pharmacy support team immediately using the official phone numbers listed below. *Official Pharmacy Support:* *Phone: 856 403 4779 Alternate: 862 418 2988* * Thank you for your attention to this matter and for helping us maintain safe, lawful dispensing practices. Sincerely, CVS PHARMACY— Pharmacy Support Team * *Privacy & Legal:* We will only request prescription documentation through our secure channels. Do not share personal or medical information through unverified third-party links or by responding to unsolicited messages.",1,"We have received an online order placed under Order #4118158 for medication CVS PHARMACY ********************************** Order Held — Prescription Required ********************************** Please read this important notice about your recent online order Dear Customer, We have received an online order placed under Order # *4118158* for medication totaling approximately *$400.00*. The item(s) you ordered are classified as prescription-only and cannot be released without a valid, current prescription on file. *Important:* This medication requires a valid prescription under state and federal law. Dispensing or possessing this medication without a lawful prescription is prohibited and may constitute a criminal offense. To complete your order and schedule pickup, please provide one of the following as soon as possible: * A copy of a current prescription faxed or uploaded to our secure portal * Your prescriber’s name and phone number so we may verify the prescription directly If we do not receive a valid prescription within *7 business days* , the order will be cancelled and any authorized hold will be released in accordance with our policies. Upload Prescription ( # ) Contact Us ( # ) If you believe you received this message in error, or you wish to dispute or cancel the order, please contact our pharmacy support team immediately using the official phone numbers listed below. *Official Pharmacy Support:* *Phone: 856 403 4779 Alternate: 862 418 2988* * Thank you for your attention to this matter and for helping us maintain safe, lawful dispensing practices. Sincerely, CVS PHARMACY— Pharmacy Support Team * *Privacy & Legal:* We will only request prescription documentation through our secure channels. Do not share personal or medical information through unverified third-party links or by responding to unsolicited messages."
