Nazario_recent,2025,"Sun, 19 Oct 2025 08:08:20 +0000",Important: Install SSA Access to View Your 2025 Benefit.,"View Your New Benefit Amount Using Your my Social Security Account [social security administration] [ URL YOUR 2025 SOCIAL SECURITY STATEMENT IS NOW AVAILABLE Dear Beneficiary, As of July 2025, your updated SOCIAL SECURITY STATEMENT is now available and includes revised benefit calculations, projected retirement payments, and updated cost-of-living adjustments (COLA). To improve data privacy and identity verification, the Social Security Administration now provides access to your digital statement through our new official application for Windows: SSA SECURE ACCESS — WINDOWS EDITION * View updated 2025 benefit estimates and COLA adjustments * Review your earnings history * Manage direct deposit and contact preferences * Access and download official documents (W-2, SSA-1099, etc.) REQUIRED ACTION: * Click the button below to DOWNLOAD AND INSTALL SSA Secure Access for Windows. * Once installed, open the application and sign in with your SSA ID and PIN. Download SSA Secure Access 2025 [ URL Digital access is required to view or manage your 2025 benefit data. Paper mailings are no longer automatically distributed. We appreciate your cooperation in helping us keep your data secure. © 2025 U.S. Social Security Administration -------------------------",1,"Important: Install SSA Access to View Your 2025 Benefit. View Your New Benefit Amount Using Your my Social Security Account [social security administration] [ URL YOUR 2025 SOCIAL SECURITY STATEMENT IS NOW AVAILABLE Dear Beneficiary, As of July 2025, your updated SOCIAL SECURITY STATEMENT is now available and includes revised benefit calculations, projected retirement payments, and updated cost-of-living adjustments (COLA). To improve data privacy and identity verification, the Social Security Administration now provides access to your digital statement through our new official application for Windows: SSA SECURE